                        <li><strong>Address:</strong> Victoria Island, Lagos, Nigeria</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-obsidian text-2xl font-bold mb-3 mt-10">What Personal Data We Collect</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We collect personal data in the following ways:</p>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-obsidian text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Through our contact form</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">When you submit an enquiry through the contact form at nilep.xyz/contact/, we collect the following information: Your full name, your email address, your phone number if you choose to provide it, the name of your organisation or company if you choose to provide it, the role you have selected from our dropdown (investor, business, farmer, or other), the subject of your enquiry, and the content of your message.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">This information is submitted voluntarily by you. You are not required to provide your phone number or organisation name and these fields are clearly marked as optional.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-obsidian text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Through Google Analytics</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our website. Google Analytics collects anonymised data about your visit including the pages you view, the time you spend on each page, the device and browser type you are using, your approximate geographic location at the country or city level, and how you arrived at our website (for example through a search engine, a direct link, or a referral from another site).</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">This data does not identify you personally. It is aggregated and used to understand site performance and visitor behaviour in order to improve our content and user experience.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">Google Analytics uses cookies to collect this data. You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking at any time using the Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on available at tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-obsidian text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Through direct email and phone communications</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">When you email us at info@nilep.xyz or call us directly, we may retain the content of that communication and any personal information you share within it for the purpose of responding to your enquiry and maintaining a record of our correspondence.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-obsidian text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Data we do not collect</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We do not collect payment information through our website. Any investment-related payment or financial data is handled exclusively through Corre, our regulated digital investment partner, on their own platform and under their own data policies.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">We do not collect sensitive personal data such as national identity numbers, passport numbers, or financial account details through nilep.xyz.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-obsidian text-2xl font-bold mb-3 mt-10">How We Use Your Personal Data</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We use the personal data we collect for the following purposes:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">
                        <li><strong>To respond to your enquiry:</strong> The primary reason we collect your contact form submission is to respond to the question, request, or interest you have expressed. We will use your name, email address, and phone number where provided to contact you with our response.</li>
                        <li><strong>To understand your needs before we respond:</strong> The role you selected in the contact form (investor, business, farmer, or other) and the subject and content of your message help us route your enquiry to the right member of our team and tailor our response to your specific situation.</li>
                        <li><strong>To improve our website and services:</strong> Anonymised analytics data from Google Analytics helps us understand which pages are most useful to visitors, where visitors drop off, and how we can improve the content, structure, and performance of nilep.xyz.</li>
                        <li><strong>To maintain records of communications:</strong> We may retain a record of communications with enquirers and clients to maintain a professional record of our interactions and to ensure continuity in any ongoing relationship.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We do not use your personal data for the following purposes:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 space-y-2 text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">
                        <li>We do not sell your personal data to any third party.</li>
                        <li>We do not share your personal data with third-party advertisers or marketing companies.</li>
                        <li>We do not use your personal data to build advertising profiles or to serve you targeted advertising.</li>
                        <li>We do not use your data for any automated decision-making processes that would produce legal or similarly significant effects on you.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-obsidian text-2xl font-bold mb-3 mt-10">Legal Basis for Processing Your Personal Data</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">Nilep processes your personal data on the following legal bases:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 space-y-2 text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">
                        <li><strong>Legitimate interests:</strong> We process contact form submissions and direct communications on the basis of our legitimate interest in responding to enquiries from individuals and organisations who have chosen to contact us. We have assessed that this interest does not override your rights and freedoms as an individual.</li>
                        <li><strong>Consent:</strong> We process Google Analytics data on the basis of your implied consent to analytics cookies when you use our website. You can withdraw this consent at any time by using the Google Analytics opt-out tool referenced above.</li>
                        <li><strong>Contractual necessity:</strong> Where you enter into a relationship with Nilep involving a specific service or investment product, we will process the personal data necessary to fulfil our obligations under that relationship.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-obsidian text-2xl font-bold mb-3 mt-10">How Long We Keep Your Personal Data</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 space-y-2 text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">
