                        <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Google Analytics data is retained according to Google's standard data retention settings, which you can review in Google's own privacy documentation. We do not independently store analytics data outside of the Google Analytics platform.</li>
                        <li><strong>Direct communications:</strong> Email and other direct communications are retained for as long as is reasonably necessary for the purpose for which they were sent, and in accordance with standard business record-keeping practices.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-obsidian text-2xl font-bold mb-3 mt-10">How We Protect Your Personal Data</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We take reasonable and appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorised access, accidental loss, alteration, or disclosure.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">Our website is served entirely over HTTPS, which encrypts all data transmitted between your browser and our site. Contact form submissions are processed through Netlify Forms, which applies its own security measures to form data in transit and at rest.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We limit access to personal data to members of our team who have a legitimate need to access it in order to respond to your enquiry or provide our services.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">While we take these precautions, no website or internet transmission is completely secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security of data transmitted to or from our site and you provide your personal information at your own risk.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-obsidian text-2xl font-bold mb-3 mt-10">Sharing Your Personal Data</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We do not sell, rent, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal data to outside parties, with the following limited exceptions:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">
