                        <li><strong>Analytics providers:</strong> We share anonymised, aggregated usage data with Google through the Google Analytics service. This data does not identify you personally. You can review Google's privacy policy at policies.google.com/privacy.</li>
                        <li><strong>Legal obligations:</strong> We may disclose your personal data if required to do so by applicable law, regulation, or a valid legal request from a government authority or court.</li>
                        <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or part of Nile Point Limited's business, your personal data may be transferred to the relevant successor entity. We would notify you of any such transfer and any choices you may have in relation to it.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">We will never share your personal data with third parties for their own marketing purposes.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-obsidian text-2xl font-bold mb-3 mt-10">Cookies</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">Nilep.xyz uses cookies to provide and improve our service.</p>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-obsidian text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2">What are cookies?</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">Cookies are small text files placed on your device by websites you visit. They are widely used to make websites work efficiently and to provide reporting information to website owners.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-obsidian text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2">The cookies we use:</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">Google Analytics cookies: These are set by Google Analytics to collect anonymised data about how visitors use our site. The main cookies used are _ga, which distinguishes unique users and expires after 2 years, and _gid, which distinguishes users and expires after 24 hours.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">We do not use advertising cookies, social media tracking cookies, or any cookies that track your activity across other websites for commercial purposes.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-obsidian text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Managing cookies:</h3>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] mb-4">You can control and delete cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to refuse cookies entirely or to be notified when a cookie is set. Please note that if you disable all cookies, some features of the site may not function as expected.</p>
                    <p class="text-secondary-custom text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-[1.8]">You can also opt out of Google Analytics specifically using the Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on at tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout.</p>
                </section>

